description: "There’s a point at 7,000 RPM where everything fades. All that’s left is a body moving through space, and time. At 7,000 RPM, that’s where you meet it.  You feel it coming, it creeps up on you close in your ear. It asks you a question, the only question that matters: Who are you?"
